    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## SMS Outreach (Outbound)\n\nRuns every 30 minutes, 9am\u20135pm NZT (NZDT).\n\n**What it does:**\n- Reads all leads from the Leads tab\n- Sends initial messages to new leads (cap: 25/run, 50/day)\n- Sends Followup 1 to leads where initial was delivered 3h+ ago, no reply\n- Sends Followup 2 to leads where F1 was delivered 21h+ ago, no reply\n- Writes PENDING to the timestamp column immediately after each send\n- Workflow 2 overwrites PENDING with confirmed timestamp on delivery, or clears it on failure\n- Waits 60s between each SMS to avoid rate limits\n\n**Why it exists:**\nAutomates the cold outreach cadence so the Mac doesn't need to stay on.",
        "height": 340,
        "width": 460,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "bb41f252-1d1d-434b-9780-9bf2e126e6be",
